      <h1 class='title'>Chemistry Teachers</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc76-7WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_76ws' title='Col. 76WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c76WS' name='column_76ws' href='#column_76ws' rel='bookmark'>76WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05007'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_389'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-bob-spink' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_389' title='Link to this speech by Dr Bob Spink' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-bob-spink" title="Dr Bob Spink">Bob Spink</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05007">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills how many teachers were in training specialising in chemistry in each of the last five years. [133864]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05008'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_390'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-miliband' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_390' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Miliband' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-miliband" title="Mr David Miliband">Mr. Miliband</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05008">The information is not available in the form requested. Numbers of funded initial teacher training places are set annually by my right hon. Friend for science as a whole. The Teacher Training Agency's annual census of recruitment to initial teacher training also collects only aggregate recruitment data for science.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05009">The table shows the number of entrants to initial teacher training courses in science since 1998/99.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_77ws' title='Col. 77WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c77WS' name='column_77ws' href='#column_77ws' rel='bookmark'>77WS</a><p id="S6CV0412P0-05010">
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Postgraduate</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Undergraduate</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Total</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1998/99</td>
          <td>2,058</td>
          <td>221</td>
          <td>2,279</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999/2000</td>
          <td>2,149</td>
          <td>213</td>
          <td>2,362</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000/01</td>
          <td>2,219</td>
          <td>191</td>
          <td>2,410</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001/02</td>
          <td>2,444</td>
          <td>150</td>
          <td>2,594</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2002/03</td>
          <td>2,568</td>
          <td>133</td>
          <td>2,701</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2003/04<sup>1</sup></td>
          <td>n/a</td>
          <td>n/a</td>
          <td>n/a</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>1</sup> The data shown above excludes trainees on the Fast Track scheme and employment based teacher training.</td>
          </tr>
          </table>
          </p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05011"><span class="italic">Source:</span></p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05012">TTA</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
